## Complete Data Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([IMAP Mailbox<br/>Multiple Accounts]) --> Fetch{Fetch New UIDs<br/>last_seen_uid+}
    Fetch --> Parse[Parse RFC822<br/>headers + body]
    Parse --> Extract[Extract<br/>external_ticket_id]
    Extract --> Match{Match Existing Ticket?}
    
    Match -->|YES - Reply| Reply[Link to Ticket<br/>email_inbox_log.ticket_id<br/>processing_result='replied']
    Match -->|NO - New| Create[Create Ticket<br/>INSERT tickets<br/>external_ticket_id=extracted<br/>issue=subject]
    
    Create --> Log1[email_inbox_log<br/>ticket_id set]
    Reply --> Log2[email_inbox_log<br/>ticket_id set]
    
    Log1 --> Notify1[Notify Admins]
    Log2 --> Notify2[Notify Admins]
    
    Create --> AutoEmail1[Auto-Email: Created]
    Create --> AutoEmail2[Auto-Email: Sent to Customer]
    
    AutoEmail2 --> Queue[email_outbox_log<br/>status=pending]
    
    Queue --> CronOut{cron/process_email_outbox.php}
    CronOut --> SMTP[SMTP Connect<br/>AUTH LOGIN<br/>DATA]
    SMTP --> Delivered[External Email<br/>Gmail/Outlook/etc.]
    
    Create --> TicketTbl[(tickets table)]
    Reply --> Update[Ticket status<br/>reopen if Closed]
    
    style Start fill:#e0f2fe
    style Fetch fill:#fef3c7
    style Parse fill:#fef3c7
    style Extract fill:#fef3c7
    style Match fill:#ddd6fe
    style Create fill:#bbf7d0
    style Reply fill:#fecaca
    style Queue fill:#fef3c7
    style CronOut fill:#e0e7ff
    style SMTP fill:#fbcfe8
    style Delivered fill:#dcfce7
    style TicketTbl fill:#f3e8ff
```

