## Inbound Processing Detail

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Raw Email<br/>RFC822] --> B[Parse Headers<br/>From, Subject, Message-ID]
    B --> C[Extract Body<br/>text/plain preferred]
    C --> D[Detect external_ticket_id<br/>Parser: 3 regex patterns]
    D --> E{Lookup:<br/>SELECT ticket_id<br/>WHERE external_ticket_id = ?}
    
    E -->|Found| F[UPDATE email_inbox_log<br/>SET ticket_id=?,<br/>processing_result='replied']
    E -->|Not Found| G[INSERT tickets<br/>issue=subject<br/>description=body<br/>external_ticket_id=detected]
    
    F --> H[Add ticket_log: 'email_reply']
    G --> I[Add ticket_log: 'created']
    
    H --> J[Notify admins]
    I --> J
    
    G --> K[Queue created email<br/>if customer_email set]
    
