## Outbound Processing Detail

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Trigger<br/>ticket created /<br/>status changed] --> B[Queue email<br/>email_smtp_queue()]
    B --> C[email_outbox_log<br/>status=pending]
    
    C --> D{cron/<br/>process_email_outbox.php}
    D --> E[Fetch 25 pending<br/>ORDER BY created_at ASC]
    E --> F[For each:<br/>Load email_account]
    
    F --> G[Connect SMTP<br/>ssl:// or tls]
    G --> H[EHLO]
    H --> I{Encryption = TLS?}
    I -->|YES| J[STARTTLS<br/>enable_crypto]
    I -->|NO| K[Skip TLS]
    J --> K
    K --> L[AUTH LOGIN<br/>base64(username+password)]
    L --> M{235?}
    M -->|Success| N[MAIL FROM /<br/>RCPT TO /<br/>DATA]
    M -->|Fail| O[Mark failed<br/>error_message]
    N --> P{Send body<br/>ends with \\r\n.}
    P -->|250| Q[Mark sent<br/>sent_at=NOW()]
    P -->|Error| O
    
    O --> R[Log ticket_log<br/>'email_failed']
    Q --> S[Log ticket_log<br/'email_sent']
    
