## Parser Pattern Matching

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Input:<br/>Subject + Body<br/>first 4000 chars] --> B[Concatenate]
    B --> C[Run 3 regex patterns]
    
    C --> D{Pattern 1:<br/>/\b(TKT-[A-Z0-9-]{2,100})\b/i}
    C --> E{Pattern 2:<br/>/(ticket|case|ref)...#([A-Z0-9-]+)/i}
    C --> F{Pattern 3:<br/>/(ticket|case|ref)...[:#-]?([A-Z0-9-]{2,})/i}
    
    D -->|Match| G[Collect TKT-XXXX]
    E -->|Match| H[Collect #ID or #TKT-ID]
    F -->|Match| I[Collect ID after separator]
    
    G --> J[Combine all matches<br/>Remove duplicates]
    H --> J
    I --> J
    
    J --> K{Normalize each:<br/>uppercase, trim,<br/>strip #}
    K --> L[Return array of candidates]
    
    L --> M{Pick first<br/>non-numeric candidate<br/>(alphanumeric > digits)}
    M -->|Found| N[external_ticket_id = candidate]
    M -->|None| O[external_ticket_id = NULL]
    
    style A fill:#e0f2fe
    style B fill:#fef3c7
    style C fill:#fef3c7
    style D fill:#ddd6fe
    style E fill:#ddd6fe
    style F fill:#ddd6fe
    style G fill:#fbcfe8
    style H fill:#fbcfe8
    style I fill:#fbcfe8
    style J fill:#fef3c7
    style K fill:#fef3c7
    style L fill:#bbf7d0
    style M fill:#ddd6fe
    style N fill:#bbf7d0
    style O fill:#fecaca
```

