## Cron Schedule

```mermaid
gantt
    title Cron Jobs Schedule
    dateFormat HH:mm
    axisFormat %H:%M
    
    section Import Inbound (IMAP)
    import_imap_tickets.php :a1, 00:00, 5m
    repeat :a1, 5m
    
    section Send Outbound (SMTP)
    process_email_outbox.php :a2, 00:00, 2m
    repeat :a2, 2m
```

**Explanation:**
- Import runs every 5 minutes → fetches new UIDs since last poll
- Outbound runs every 2 minutes → sends up to 25 pending emails

Both are idempotent (safe to re-run).

