## Data Transformations

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Inbound: Email → Ticket"
        A1[Raw RFC822] --> A2[Parse]
        A2 --> A3[extract external_ticket_id]
        A3 --> A4{Exists?}
        A4 -->|Yes| A5[Link as reply<br/>ticket_id set]
        A4 -->|No| A6[Create new ticket<br/>external_ticket_id=extracted<br/>issue=subject]
    end
    
    subgraph "Outbound: Ticket → Email"
        B1[Ticket status change] --> B2{Which status?}
        B2 -->|Open| B3[No email]
        B2 -->|In-Progress| B4[Queue In-Progress email]
        B2 -->|Closed| B5[Queue Closed email]
        B4 --> B6[email_outbox_log]
        B5 --> B6
        B6 --> B7[Cron sends]
        B7 --> B8[External inbox]
    end
    
    subgraph "Manual"
        C1[Compose form] --> C2[Ticket selector → ticket_id]
        C2 --> C3[email_outbox_log with ticket_id]
        C3 --> B7
    end
    
