## Troubleshooting Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Email issue reported] --> B{What's the symptom?}
    
    B -->|Not sending| C[Check Outbox status]
    C --> D{pending?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Cron running?<br/>Check last_checked_at]
    E -->|No| F[Start cron job<br/>php cron/import_imap_tickets.php]
    E -->|Yes| G[Check SMTP config<br/>Dashboard → Test SMTP]
    
    D -->|Failed| H[Read error_message]
    H --> I{Error type}
    I -->|"greeting"| J[Fix: smtp_encryption='ssl'<br/>for port 465]
    I -->|"Authentication"| K[Update password<br/>in accounts.php]
    I -->|"Permission"| L[Ask hosting to<br/>open outbound port]
    I -->|Other| M[Check logs<br/>tail error_log]
    
    B -->|Not creating ticket| N[Check inbox_log]
    N --> O{processing_result}
    O -->|ignored| P[Check ignored_reason<br/>likely: no ID + no issue]
    O -->|pending| Q[Cron down?<br/>Run import manually]
    O -->|created/replied| R[Working fine<br/>check ticket_id link]
    
    B -->|Spam folder| S[SPF/DKIM missing<br/>Add DNS records]
    
    style A fill:#e0f2fe
